Looking into [StackOverflow|https://stackoverflow.com/questions/40674526/bitbucket-pipelines-heroku-deploy-issue] threads, we found that the cause may be the Secured Environment variable, the solution proposed there is to store it in plain text, which is not the best option since it exposes the secret KEY.

